    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "gini_index"
      ],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "Gini(S) = 1 - \\sum_i p_i^2",
        "spoken": "基尼指数等于1减去每个类别概率的平方和。"
      },
      "id": "s036",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "基尼指数的公式是：",
        "$$ Gini(S) = 1 - \\sum_i p_i^2 $$"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "gini_index"
      ],
      "id": "s037",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "当所有样本属于同一类时，基尼指数为0。",
        "当样本均匀分布在各类时，基尼指数最大。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "overfitting"
      ],
      "id": "s038",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "overfitting"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "决策树可以长得很深，直到每个叶子都纯。",
        "但这可能导致<term id=\"overfitting\">过拟合</term>。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "overfitting"
      ],
      "id": "s039",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "过拟合的模型记住了训练数据的细节和噪声。",
        "它在训练集上表现完美，但在新数据上表现很差。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "underfitting"
      ],
      "id": "s040",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "underfitting"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "相反，如果树太浅，可能连训练数据都学不好。",
        "这叫<term id=\"underfitting\">欠拟合</term>。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "pruning"
      ],
      "id": "s041",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "pruning"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "解决过拟合的一种方法是<term id=\"pruning\">剪枝</term>。",
        "先让树完全生长，然后从底部剪掉一些分支。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "pruning"
      ],
      "id": "s042",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "剪枝时，用一个叶子节点替代一个子树。",
        "如果剪掉后模型在验证集上表现更好，就保留剪枝。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
